Sentencas: This article presents elaboration of electrolyte-supported solid oxide fuel cells based on the oxide ion conductor BaIn0.3Ti0.7O2.85 (BIT07) as electrolyte, the amorphous reduced phase of La2Mo2O9 (La2Mo2O7-y) as anode which presents a mixed ionic and electronic conduction in low pO(2) and La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-delta (LSCF) as cathode.
Titulo: Innovative solid oxide fuel cells based on BaIn0.3Ti0.7O2.85 electrolyte and La2Mo2O9 amorphous reduced phase as anode material

Sentencas: Electrode materials have been deposited by screen-printing on BITO7 substrate.
Titulo: Innovative solid oxide fuel cells based on BaIn0.3Ti0.7O2.85 electrolyte and La2Mo2O9 amorphous reduced phase as anode material

Sentencas: In order to avoid chemical reactivity between BITO7 and La2Mo2O9, a thin layer of Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 (CGO) has been used.
Titulo: Innovative solid oxide fuel cells based on BaIn0.3Ti0.7O2.85 electrolyte and La2Mo2O9 amorphous reduced phase as anode material

Sentencas: Electrochemical performance of the single cell has been characterized by I-V measurements and impedance spectroscopy.
Titulo: Innovative solid oxide fuel cells based on BaIn0.3Ti0.7O2.85 electrolyte and La2Mo2O9 amorphous reduced phase as anode material

Sentencas: Encouraging performance of 40 mW cm(-2) at 700 degrees C is obtained with a thick electrolyte layer.
Titulo: Innovative solid oxide fuel cells based on BaIn0.3Ti0.7O2.85 electrolyte and La2Mo2O9 amorphous reduced phase as anode material

Sentencas: Finally, ageing test of the cell at 700 degrees C during 800 h has been done with a low rate of performance loss of 4.4 x 10(-3)% h(-1).
Titulo: Innovative solid oxide fuel cells based on BaIn0.3Ti0.7O2.85 electrolyte and La2Mo2O9 amorphous reduced phase as anode material

Sentencas: No degradation of the electrolyte material is reported and stability of the anode material after operating the fuel cell is discussed.
Titulo: Innovative solid oxide fuel cells based on BaIn0.3Ti0.7O2.85 electrolyte and La2Mo2O9 amorphous reduced phase as anode material
